    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Waiting for a Leader'' (editorial, Sept. 1):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Waiting for a Leader'' (editorial, Sept. 1):</p>
        <p>The tragedy of Hurricane Katrina might become the catalyst for alerting Americans to the broader inadequacies of the Bush administration.</p>
        <p>We should begin to wonder about our leaders' resistance to warnings about the dangers of global warming. We might also question the need for a senseless war in Iraq, with its high human and financial costs.</p>
        <p>If the present policy continues, I am afraid that we may not be able to respond adequately to disasters in the future.</p>
        <p>Pearl Volkov  Sun City Center, Fla., Sept. 1, 2005</p>
      </block>
